Description: Vertex theme for GTK 3, GTK 2, Gnome-Shell and Cinnamon
 Vertex is a theme for GTK 3, GTK 2, Gnome-Shell and Cinnamon.
 .
 This package installs three variants to choose from: the default with dark
 header-bars, a light variant, and a dark variant.
